ReadMe
Welcome to Azure Monitor Challenge.

As part of the Azure Monitor Challenge, the participants will learn the enablement of the Azure Monitor for SAP On Azure deployment.

Scenario#
One of Microsoft customers migrated the first waves of SAP Landscape on Azure, and one of the requirements from stakeholders is to configure Azure native services for Monitoring the solution.

Challenges#
1. Deploy SAP On Azure monitoring solution with OS & SAP NetWeaver providers. 
2. Configure log analytics workspace and review the stats for troubleshooting using Kusto query. 

Tasks#
Task1: Create a Log Analytics Workspace. 
Task2: Deploy Azure Monitor for SAP. 
Task3: Enable VM Insights on Virtual Machines running SAP Workloads and connect to log analytics workspace created as part of Task1. 
Task4: Configure OS, SAP NetWeaver providers. 
Task5: Check for Monitoring data in Log Analytics Workspace. 
Task6: Use Kusto query to create custom dashboard and setup alerts.



Reference:
https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/virtual-machines/workloads/sap/azure-monitor-overview
https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/azure-monitor/vm/vminsights-enable-overview
